*Kažemo* da će vremenske prilike biti dobre. (We say that the weather will be good.)

Neko će *kažemu* da to nije istina. (Someone will say to him that this is not true.)

Svi *kažemo* da je to nemoguće. (We all say that it is impossible.)

*Kažemo* se da je on veoma pametan. (It is said that he is very smart.)

*Kažemu* se da je to veoma teško. (It is said that this is very hard.)